    "# Step 1: 确定节假日的起始和结束日期\n",
    "def get_holiday_ranges(holiday_dates):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    输入：一个包含所有节假日的日期列表\n",
    "    输出：节假日区间 (起始日, 结束日) 的列表\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    holiday_dates = sorted(holiday_dates)  # 确保节假日按日期排序\n",
    "    ranges = []  # 保存节假日区间\n",
    "    start_date = holiday_dates[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "    for i in range(1, len(holiday_dates)):\n",
    "        # 如果当前日期不连续（间隔超过1天），则记录当前区间\n",
    "        if (holiday_dates[i] - holiday_dates[i - 1]).days > 1:\n",
    "            ranges.append((start_date, holiday_dates[i - 1]))  # 记录当前区间\n",
    "            start_date = holiday_dates[i]  # 更新起始日期\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 添加最后一个区间\n",
    "    ranges.append((start_date, holiday_dates[-1]))\n",
    "    return ranges"
   ]

    "# Step 2: 标记节假日前后\n",
    "def mark_pre_post_holiday(data, holiday_ranges):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    根据节假日区间标记节假日前一天和节假日后一天\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    data[\"is_pre_holiday\"] = False\n",
    "    data[\"is_post_holiday\"] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "    for start_date, end_date in holiday_ranges:\n",
    "        # 标记节假日前一天\n",
    "        pre_holiday_date = start_date - pd.Timedelta(days=1)\n",
    "        if pre_holiday_date in data[\"date\"].values:\n",
    "            data.loc[data[\"date\"] == pre_holiday_date, \"is_pre_holiday\"] = True\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 标记节假日后一天\n",
    "        post_holiday_date = end_date + pd.Timedelta(days=1)\n",
    "        if post_holiday_date in data[\"date\"].values:\n",
    "            data.loc[data[\"date\"] == post_holiday_date, \"is_post_holiday\"] = True\n",
    "\n",
    "    return data\n"
   ]

    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "# Step 1: 创建日历表\n",
    "# 假设从2022年到2024年\n",
    "start_date = \"2022-01-01\"\n",
    "end_date = \"2024-12-31\"\n",
    "calendar = pd.DataFrame({\"date\": pd.date_range(start=start_date, end=end_date, freq=\"D\")})\n",
    "calendar[\"is_workday\"] = ~calendar[\"date\"].dt.weekday.isin([5, 6])  # 非周末为工作日\n",
    "\n",
    "# Step 2: 根据元组列表生成节日日期\n",
    "def generate_holidays(years, holiday_tuples):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    根据给定的年份和节日元组列表生成节日日期\n",
    "    :param years: 年份列表，例如 [2022, 2023, 2024]\n",
    "    :param holiday_tuples: 节日日期元组列表，例如 [(1, 1), (5, 1), (10, 1)]\n",
    "    :return: 节日日期列表\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    holidays_dates = []\n",
    "    for year in years:\n",
    "        for month, day in holiday_tuples:\n",
    "            holidays_dates.append(pd.Timestamp(year, month, day))\n",
    "    return holidays_dates\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义节日元组列表\n",
    "holiday_tuples = [(1, 1), (5, 1), (10, 1)]  # 元旦、劳动节、国庆节\n",
    "years = [2022, 2023, 2024]\n",
    "holidays_dates = generate_holidays(years, holiday_tuples)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 标记节假日\n",
    "calendar[\"is_holiday\"] = calendar[\"date\"].isin(holidays_dates)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Step 3: 搜索节日前后的第一个工作日\n",
    "def find_nearest_workday(calendar, holidays_dates):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    找到节日前后的第一个工作日\n",
    "    :param calendar: 包含日期和工作日信息的 DataFrame\n",
    "    :param holidays_dates: 节日日期列表\n",
    "    :return: 更新后的 DataFrame，包含 is_pre_holiday 和 is_post_holiday 标记\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    calendar[\"is_pre_holiday\"] = False\n",
    "    calendar[\"is_post_holiday\"] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "    for holiday in holidays_dates:\n",
    "        # 向前找最近的工作日\n",
    "        pre_workday = calendar[(calendar[\"date\"] < holiday) & (calendar[\"is_workday\"])].iloc[-1:]\n",
    "        if not pre_workday.empty:\n",
    "            calendar.loc[calendar[\"date\"] == pre_workday[\"date\"].values[0], \"is_pre_holiday\"] = True\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 向后找最近的工作日\n",
    "        post_workday = calendar[(calendar[\"date\"] > holiday) & (calendar[\"is_workday\"])].iloc[0:1]\n",
    "        if not post_workday.empty:\n",
    "            calendar.loc[calendar[\"date\"] == post_workday[\"date\"].values[0], \"is_post_holiday\"] = True\n",
    "\n",
    "    return calendar\n",
    "\n",
    "# 应用节日前后工作日标记\n",
    "calendar = find_nearest_workday(calendar, holidays_dates)\n"
   ]
  },

    "# 模拟节假日前后 1 天数据的剧烈波动\n",

    "cn_holidays_2024 = holidays.China(years=[2024])\n",
    "\n",
    "all_holidays = list(cn_holidays_2021) + list(cn_holidays_2022) + list(cn_holidays_2023) + list(cn_holidays_2024)\n",

    "# Step 1: 模拟数据生成\n",

    "dates = pd.date_range(start=\"2022-01-01\", end=\"2024-12-31\", freq=\"B\")  # 仅生成工作日\n",
    "# 从dates中删除all_holidays中的日期\n",
    "dates = dates[~dates.isin(all_holidays)]\n",
    "data = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    \"date\": dates,\n",

    "# Step 3: 加入往年节假日对应工作日的销量比值特征\n",
    "def calculate_holiday_ratio(data, holiday_dates, near_mode='pre', feature_col=\"in\", weights=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算节假日与往年节假日销量的加权比值特征\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    if weights is None:\n",
    "        weights = [0.35, 0.35, 0.15, 0.15]  # 默认权重分配\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 初始化特征列\n",
    "    data[f\"{feature_col}_{near_mode}_holiday_ratio_feature\"] = 0.0\n",
    "\n",
    "    for holiday_date in holiday_dates:\n",
    "        # 因为节假日本身不在数据中，所以判断preday or post_day是否在数据中\n",
    "        if near_mode == 'pre':\n",
    "            near_holiday_date = holiday_date-timedelta(days=1)\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            near_holiday_date = holiday_date+timedelta(days=1)\n",
    "        near_holiday_date = near_holiday_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n",
    "\n",
    "        \n",
    "        date_list = data[\"date\"].values\n",
    "        date_list = [pd.to_datetime(date).strftime('%Y-%m-%d') for date in date_list]\n",
    "        if near_holiday_date in date_list:\n",
    "            # 找到当前near_day的索引\n",
    "            near_holiday_idx = data[data[\"date\"] == near_holiday_date].index[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "            # 获取前后交易日索引\n",
    "            key_indices = []\n",
    "            for offset in [-10, -5, 5, 10]:  # 前后两周\n",
    "                idx = near_holiday_idx + offset\n",
    "                if 0 <= idx < len(data):  # 确保索引合法\n",
    "                    key_indices.append(idx)\n",
    "                    \n",
    "            # 确保交易日数量与权重一致\n",
    "            key_indices = key_indices[:len(weights)]\n",
    "            valid_weights = weights[:len(key_indices)]\n",
    "\n",
    "            # 加权平均值计算\n",
    "            weighted_sum = 0\n",
    "            total_weight = 0\n",
    "            for i, key_idx in enumerate(key_indices):\n",
    "                if 0 <= key_idx < len(data):  # 确保索引合法\n",
    "                    key_value = data.iloc[key_idx][feature_col]\n",
    "                    weighted_sum += key_value * valid_weights[i]\n",
    "                    total_weight += valid_weights[i]\n",
    "\n",
    "            # 当前节假日销量\n",
    "            holiday_value = data.loc[near_holiday_idx, feature_col]\n",
    "\n",
    "            # 计算加权比值特征\n",
    "            if total_weight > 0:\n",
    "                ratio = holiday_value / (weighted_sum / total_weight)\n",
    "                data.loc[data[\"date\"] == near_holiday_date, f\"{feature_col}_{near_mode}_holiday_ratio_feature\"] = ratio\n",
    "\n",
    "    return data"
   ]

   "source": [
    "# Step 4: 构造训练集和测试集\n",
    "features = [col for col in data.columns if col not in [\"date\", \"in\", \"out\"]]\n",
    "X = data[features]\n",
    "y_purchase = data[\"in\"]\n",
    "y_redemption = data[\"out\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "X_train, X_test, y_train_purchase, y_test_purchase = train_test_split(X, y_purchase, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)\n",
    "X_train, X_test, y_train_redemption, y_test_redemption = train_test_split(X, y_redemption, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)"
   ]

    "# Step 5: 模型训练\n",
    "purchase_model = XGBRegressor(\n",
    "    max_depth=3,\n",
    "    learning_rate=0.05,\n",
    "    n_estimators=500,\n",
    "    reg_alpha=10,\n",
    "    gamma=1,\n",
    "    random_state=42,\n",
    "    objective='reg:squarederror'\n",
    ")\n",
    "redemption_model = XGBRegressor(\n",
    "    max_depth=3,\n",
    "    learning_rate=0.05,\n",
    "    n_estimators=500,\n",
    "    reg_alpha=10,\n",
    "    gamma=1,\n",
    "    random_state=42\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "purchase_model.fit(X_train, y_train_purchase)\n",
    "redemption_model.fit(X_train, y_train_redemption)"
   ]
